<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>网易云音乐「每日推荐」PRD + 交互原型</title>
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #fff; --text: #1a1a2e; --text2: #666; --border: #e8e8e8;
  --accent: #c10d0d; --accent2: #ec4141; --card: #fafafa;
  --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  --tag-bg: #fef0f0; --tag-text: #c10d0d;
  --code-bg: #f5f5f5; --phone-bg: #f0f0f0;
}
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --bg: #1a1a2e; --text: #e8e8e8; --text2: #999; --border: #333;
    --accent: #ec4141; --accent2: #ff5252; --card: #222;
    --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    --tag-bg: #3a1a1a; --code-bg: #2a2a3a; --phone-bg: #111;
  }
}
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height:1.7; }
.container { max-width: 900px; margin:0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; }

/* PRD sections */
.prd-header { text-align:center; padding:60px 0 40px; border-bottom:2px solid var(--accent); margin-bottom:40px; }
.prd-header h1 { font-size:32px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:8px; }
.prd-header .meta { color:var(--text2); font-size:14px; }
.prd-header .meta span { margin:0 12px; }

section { margin-bottom:48px; }
section h2 { font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:20px; padding-bottom:10px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
section h2 .num { background:var(--accent); color:#fff; width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:14px; flex-shrink:0; }
section h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:600; margin:16px 0 8px; }
section p { margin-bottom:12px; color:var(--text2); }

.tag { display:inline-block; background:var(--tag-bg); color:var(--tag-text); padding:2px 10px; border-radius:12px; font-size:13px; margin:2px 4px; }
.card { background:var(--card); border-radius:12px; padding:24px; margin:16px 0; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
.card h4 { font-size:15px; margin-bottom:8px; }

/* Flow diagram */
.flow { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; padding:20px; background:var(--card); border-radius:12px; margin:16px 0; font-size:14px; overflow-x:auto; }
.flow .node { background:var(--accent); color:#fff; padding:8px 16px; border-radius:8px; white-space:nowrap; }
.flow .arrow { color:var(--accent); font-weight:bold; }
.flow .node.secondary { background:#555; }
.flow .branch { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px; }

/* Table */
table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin:16px 0; font-size:14px; }
th, td { padding:10px 14px; text-align:left; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
th { background:var(--card); font-weight:600; }
tr:hover { background:var(--card); }

/* Prototype section */
.phone-wrapper { display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; padding:20px; background:var(--phone-bg); border-radius:16px; }
.phone { width:375px; height:750px; background:#121212; border-radius:32px; overflow:hidden; position:relative; box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 0 3px #333, 0 0 0 6px #1a1a1a; }
.phone-screen { width:100%; height:100%; background:#1a1a1a; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
.phone-screen.light { background:#f5f5f5; }
.phone-notch { position:absolute; top:0; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:120px; height:28px; background:#000; border-radius:0 0 16px 16px; z-index:100; }

/* List Page */
.page { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; transition:transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.8,0.25,1); display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
.page.hidden-left { transform:translateX(-100%); }
.page.hidden-right { transform:translateX(100%); }
.page.hidden-bottom { transform:translateY(100%); }

.page-header { padding:40px 20px 12px; text-align:center; position:relative; z-index:2; }
.page-header .date { font-size:13px; color:#999; margin-bottom:2px; }
.page-header .title { font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; }
.page-header .cover-bg { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; filter:blur(40px) brightness(0.4); z-index:-1; }
.play-all { margin:12px 20px; padding:10px 0; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c10d0d,#ec4141); border-radius:24px; text-align:center; color:#fff; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; transition:transform 0.15s, opacity 0.15s; }
.play-all:active { transform:scale(0.97); opacity:0.85; }

.song-list { flex:1; overflow-y:auto; padding:0 16px 20px; -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch; }
.song-list::-webkit-scrollbar { width:0; }
.song-item { display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 8px; border-radius:10px; position:relative; cursor:pointer; touch-action:pan-y; user-select:none; transition:transform 0.25s, background 0.2s; }
.song-item:active { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
.song-item .idx { width:28px; text-align:center; font-size:13px; color:#888; flex-shrink:0; }
.song-item .cover { width:44px; height:44px; border-radius:6px; background:#333; flex-shrink:0; object-fit:cover; }
.song-item .info { flex:1; margin-left:10px; min-width:0; }
.song-item .info .name { font-size:14px; color:#eee; white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; }
.song-item .info .artist { font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-top:2px; }
.song-item .dur { font-size:12px; color:#666; margin:0 8px; }

.swipe-bg { position:absolute; top:0; height:100%; display:flex; align-items:center; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; padding:0 20px; border-radius:10px; z-index:-1; }
.swipe-bg.left { right:0; background:#c10d0d; color:#fff; border-radius:0 10px 10px 0; }
.swipe-bg.right { left:0; background:#ec4141; color:#fff; border-radius:10px 0 0 10px; }

/* Player Page */
.player-bg { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; filter:blur(60px) brightness(0.25); z-index:0; }
.player-content { position:relative; z-index:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; height:100%; padding-top:40px; }
.player-top { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding:0 20px; }
.player-top .back { width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:50%; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; cursor:pointer; font-size:18px; color:#fff; transition:background 0.2s; }
.player-top .back:active { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
.player-top .share { color:#fff; font-size:13px; opacity:0.7; cursor:pointer; }

.player-disc { flex:1; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; position:relative; }
.player-disc .disc { width:220px; height:220px; border-radius:50%; position:relative; }
.player-disc .disc img { width:100%; height:100%; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; }
.player-disc .disc.spinning { animation:spin 20s linear infinite; }
@keyframes spin { to { transform:rotate(360deg); } }
.player-disc .disc.paused { animation-play-state:paused; }
.player-disc .disc-hole { position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); width:52px; height:52px; border-radius:50%; background:#1a1a1a; border:3px solid #333; }
.player-disc .arm { position:absolute; top:-20px; right:-40px; width:80px; height:120px; z-index:5; transition:transform 0.5s; }
.player-disc .arm.playing { transform:rotate(-15deg); }

.lyric-area { height:100px; overflow:hidden; text-align:center; padding:0 30px; position:relative; }
.lyric-area .lyric-line { color:#666; font-size:14px; padding:6px 0; transition:all 0.4s; }
.lyric-area .lyric-line.active { color:#fff; font-size:16px; font-weight:600; }

.player-controls { padding:0 30px 20px; }
.progress-bar { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; margin-bottom:16px; }
.progress-bar .time { font-size:11px; color:#888; width:36px; }
.progress-bar .track { flex:1; height:3px; background:#444; border-radius:2px; position:relative; cursor:pointer; }
.progress-bar .track-fill { height:100%; background:#c10d0d; border-radius:2px; width:35%; }
.progress-bar .track-thumb { position:absolute; top:50%; left:35%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); width:12px; height:12px; background:#fff; border-radius:50%; }

.ctrl-btns { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:20px; }
.ctrl-btns .btn { color:#ccc; font-size:18px; cursor:pointer; padding:8px; transition:color 0.15s; }
.ctrl-btns .btn:active { color:#fff; }
.ctrl-btns .btn-play { width:56px; height:56px; border-radius:50%; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c10d0d,#ec4141); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:22px; color:#fff; cursor:pointer; transition:transform 0.15s; }
.ctrl-btns .btn-play:active { transform:scale(0.92); }

.actions { display:flex; justify-content:space-around; }
.actions .act { color:#888; font-size:12px; text-align:center; cursor:pointer; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:4px; transition:color 0.15s; }
.actions .act:active { color:#fff; }
.actions .act .icon { font-size:18px; }
.actions .act.liked { color:#ec4141; }

/* Feedback Modal */
.modal-mask { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index:50; transition:opacity 0.3s; opacity:0; pointer-events:none; }
.modal-mask.show { opacity:1; pointer-events:auto; }
.modal-sheet { position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; width:100%; background:#1e1e1e; border-radius:20px 20px 0 0; padding:24px 20px 40px; transform:translateY(100%); transition:transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.32,0.72,0,1); }
.modal-mask.show .modal-sheet { transform:translateY(0); }
.modal-sheet h4 { color:#fff; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:16px; }
.modal-sheet .reason-grid { display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:20px; }
.modal-sheet .reason-chip { padding:10px 18px; border-radius:20px; border:1px solid #444; color:#ccc; font-size:13px; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; }
.modal-sheet .reason-chip.selected { background:rgba(193,13,13,0.2); border-color:#c10d0d; color:#c10d0d; }
.modal-sheet textarea { width:100%; height:60px; background:#2a2a2a; border:1px solid #444; border-radius:10px; color:#fff; padding:12px; font-size:13px; resize:none; outline:none; font-family:inherit; margin-bottom:16px; }
.modal-sheet textarea:focus { border-color:#c10d0d; }
.modal-sheet .submit-row { display:flex; gap:12px; }
.modal-sheet .submit-row button { flex:1; padding:12px; border-radius:24px; border:none; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; transition:transform 0.15s; }
.modal-sheet .submit-row button:active { transform:scale(0.96); }
.modal-sheet .submit-row .btn-skip { background:#333; color:#ccc; }
.modal-sheet .submit-row .btn-submit { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c10d0d,#ec4141); color:#fff; }

.toast { position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); background:rgba(0,0,0,0.85); color:#fff; padding:12px 28px; border-radius:20px; font-size:14px; z-index:100; opacity:0; transition:opacity 0.3s; pointer-events:none; }
.toast.show { opacity:1; }

/* Page tabs */
.page-tabs { display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:16px 0 0; }
.page-tabs .tab { padding:6px 16px; border-radius:16px; font-size:12px; cursor:pointer; background:#333; color:#aaa; border:none; transition:all 0.2s; }
.page-tabs .tab.active { background:var(--accent); color:#fff; }

/* Skeleton */
.skeleton { background:linear-gradient(90deg,#2a2a2a 25%,#333 50%,#2a2a2a 75%); background-size:200% 100%; animation:shimmer 1.5s infinite; border-radius:6px; }
@keyframes shimmer { 0% { background-position:200% 0; } 100% { background-position:-200% 0; } }

.metric-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr)); gap:12px; }
.metric-card { background:var(--card); border-radius:12px; padding:20px; text-align:center; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
.metric-card .value { font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent); }
.metric-card .label { font-size:13px; color:var(--text2); margin-top:4px; }

.legend { display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:24px; font-size:12px; color:var(--text2); margin-top:8px; }
.legend span::before { content:''; display:inline-block; width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:50%; margin-right:5px; }
.legend .like::before { background:#ec4141; }
.legend .dislike::before { background:#c10d0d; }

pre { background:var(--code-bg); border-radius:8px; padding:16px; overflow-x:auto; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

<!-- PRD Header -->
<header class="prd-header">
  <h1>网易云音乐「每日推荐」歌单模块</h1>
  <p class="meta">产品需求文档 + 交互原型 <span>|</span> 2026-05-19 <span>|</span> 面试作品 v1.0</p>
</header>

<!-- 1. 背景与目标 -->
<section>
  <h2><span class="num">1</span>背景与目标</h2>

  <h3>项目背景</h3>
  <p>「每日推荐」是网易云音乐日活最高的核心模块之一，每天为 3000 万+ 用户生成个性化推荐歌单。当前模块存在三个问题：列表页反馈路径深（需进入三级菜单）、播放页信息层级拥挤、负反馈收集粗糙（仅"不喜欢"二值判断），导致推荐模型收到的信号质量低，用户满意度停滞。</p>

  <h3>产品目标</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <h4>核心指标</h4>
    <table>
      <tr><th>指标</th><th>现状</th><th>目标</th><th>衡量方式</th></tr>
      <tr><td>每日推荐完播率</td><td>58%</td><td>≥ 72%</td><td>播放完成占比</td></tr>
      <tr><td>负反馈收集率</td><td>3.2%</td><td>≥ 15%</td><td>不感兴趣操作占比</td></tr>
      <tr><td>推荐满意度 NPS</td><td>38</td><td>≥ 50</td><td>季度用户调研</td></tr>
      <tr><td>次日留存</td><td>62%</td><td>≥ 70%</td><td>隔日回访用户占比</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h3>设计原则</h3>
  <p>轻反馈、重感知——让用户在听歌过程中自然表达偏好，而非打断流量填问卷。所有操作 ≤ 2 步完成。</p>
</section>

<!-- 2. 用户场景 -->
<section>
  <h2><span class="num">2</span>用户场景</h2>

  <div class="card">
    <h4>场景一：晨间通勤 — 快速发现新歌</h4>
    <p>小张，28 岁，互联网运营。每天 8:30 地铁通勤 40 分钟，打开网易云「每日推荐」，从 30 首里挑 5-6 首喜欢的加入歌单，遇到不喜欢的快速跳过。诉求：操作快、加载快、离线可听。</p>
    <span class="tag">通勤场景</span><span class="tag">快速筛选</span><span class="tag">离线缓存</span>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h4>场景二：深夜独处 — 沉浸式听歌</h4>
    <p>小李，22 岁，大学生。睡前刷每日推荐，切到播放页沉浸式听完整首，看歌词、看评论。偶尔遇到很喜欢的会分享到朋友圈。诉求：沉浸感强、歌词精准、社交分享。</p>
    <span class="tag">沉浸消费</span><span class="tag">歌词场景</span><span class="tag">社交传播</span>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h4>场景三：干活背景音 — 长时播放 + 偶发反馈</h4>
    <p>小王，31 岁，设计师。工作时打开每日推荐当背景音，偶尔注意到不喜欢的歌才会点一下反馈，不想打断工作流。诉求：无操作自动续播、反馈路径短。</p>
    <span class="tag">后台播放</span><span class="tag">低打扰</span><span class="tag">自动续播</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 3. 信息架构 & 页面流 -->
<section>
  <h2><span class="num">3</span>信息架构 &amp; 页面流</h2>

  <div class="flow">
    <div class="node">每日推荐入口</div>
    <span class="arrow">→</span>
    <div class="node">列表页<br><small>30首每日推荐</small></div>
    <span class="arrow">→</span>
    <div class="branch">
      <span style="color:#c10d0d;font-size:12px;">点击歌曲</span>
      <span style="color:#ec4141;font-size:12px;">左滑不感兴趣</span>
      <span style="color:#fff;font-size:12px;">右滑收藏</span>
    </div>
    <span class="arrow">→</span>
    <div class="node">播放页<br><small>全屏沉浸</small></div>
    <span class="arrow">↔</span>
    <div class="node secondary">反馈弹窗<br><small>半屏滑出</small></div>
  </div>

  <p>列表页是信息枢纽，播放页是消费终点，反馈弹窗是双向信令通道——用户的每一次反馈同时更新前端 UI 和云端推荐模型。</p>

  <h3>状态流转</h3>
  <div class="flow">
    <div class="node">加载中</div><span class="arrow">→</span>
    <div class="node">有数据</div><span class="arrow">→</span>
    <div class="node">列表页</div>
  </div>
  <div class="flow" style="margin-top:8px;">
    <div class="node secondary">加载超时</div><span class="arrow">→</span>
    <div class="node secondary">重试页</div>
  </div>
  <div class="flow" style="margin-top:8px;">
    <div class="node secondary">今日无数据</div><span class="arrow">→</span>
    <div class="node secondary">空状态页</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 4. 视觉与交互细节 -->
<section>
  <h2><span class="num">4</span>视觉与交互细节</h2>

  <h3>列表页</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <ul style="padding-left:20px;color:var(--text2);font-size:14px;line-height:2;">
      <li>顶部日期标识 + 封面提取主色渐变背景，营造每日新鲜感</li>
      <li>歌曲行高 64px，封面 44×44 圆角 6px，歌名 14px 白色，歌手 12px #888</li>
      <li>时长右对齐，12px #666，格式 m:ss</li>
      <li><strong>左滑手势</strong>：主行左移露出红色「不感兴趣」底，释放后触发反馈弹窗</li>
      <li><strong>右滑手势</strong>：主行右移露出红色心形底，释放后收藏（心形填充动画）</li>
      <li>播放全部按钮悬浮于列表上方，毛玻璃半透明背景</li>
      <li>下拉刷新（Pull to Refresh）重新请求今日推荐</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3>播放页</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <ul style="padding-left:20px;color:var(--text2);font-size:14px;line-height:2;">
      <li>全屏暗色 + 封面毛玻璃 blur(60px) + brightness(0.25) 背景</li>
      <li>黑胶唱片 220px 居中旋转（播放态 20s/圈），暂停态停止旋转</li>
      <li>唱片中央 52px 圆孔 + 金属边框，右侧唱臂随播放/暂停摆入/摆出</li>
      <li>歌词区域 100px，当前行 16px 白色加粗，前后行 14px 半透明</li>
      <li>进度条可拖拽，已播部分主题色，未播部分 #444</li>
      <li>底部：上一首 | 播放/暂停（56px 主题色圆按钮）| 下一首</li>
      <li>操作栏：收藏（已收藏红色实心）、下载、评论、分享</li>
      <li>左滑切换至下一首，右滑提示反馈弹窗</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3>反馈弹窗</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <ul style="padding-left:20px;color:var(--text2);font-size:14px;line-height:2;">
      <li>底部半屏滑出，背景 rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 半透明遮罩，点击遮罩关闭</li>
      <li>标题「告诉我们你不喜欢这首歌的原因」</li>
      <li>快捷原因：<span class="tag">不感兴趣</span><span class="tag">听腻了</span><span class="tag">质量差</span> — 多选 Chip</li>
      <li>补充输入框（选填，60px 高度，placeholder「补充更多原因…」）</li>
